1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,251
Welcome to the Somatic Healing Body Scan.

2
00:00:15,251 --> 00:00:15,251
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

3
00:00:15,251 --> 00:00:21,047
This practice invites you to listen to
the body as a messenger of parts,

4
00:00:21,047 --> 00:00:23,006
protection, and emotion.

5
00:00:23,006 --> 00:00:25,421
It is not a medical assessment.

6
00:00:25,421 --> 00:00:28,440
It is a gentle awareness practice.

7
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:30,901
Begin by getting comfortable.

8
00:00:30,901 --> 00:00:33,780
Let your body be supported.

9
00:00:33,780 --> 00:00:36,195
Take a slow breath in.

10
00:00:45,195 --> 00:00:45,195
<break time="3s" />

11
00:00:45,195 --> 00:00:47,285
And let it out.

12
00:00:47,285 --> 00:00:50,582
Now bring attention to the top of your
head.

13
00:01:02,582 --> 00:01:02,582
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

14
00:01:02,582 --> 00:01:04,765
Notice any sensation there.

15
00:01:04,765 --> 00:01:06,855
No need to change it.

16
00:01:06,855 --> 00:01:09,409
Move attention to your forehead.

17
00:01:09,409 --> 00:01:10,756
Your eyes.

18
00:01:10,756 --> 00:01:11,963
Your jaw.

19
00:01:11,963 --> 00:01:13,496
Your mouth.

20
00:01:13,496 --> 00:01:18,837
Notice softness, tension, numbness, or
movement.

21
00:01:18,837 --> 00:01:20,648
Now the throat.

22
00:01:20,648 --> 00:01:25,664
Ask: Is there anything here that wants to
be noticed?

23
00:01:37,664 --> 00:01:37,664
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

24
00:01:37,664 --> 00:01:39,336
Move to the shoulders.

25
00:01:39,336 --> 00:01:41,565
Notice what they carry.

26
00:01:41,565 --> 00:01:43,098
Move to the chest.

27
00:01:43,098 --> 00:01:50,761
Notice breath, tightness, openness,
heaviness, warmth, or emptiness.

28
00:01:50,761 --> 00:01:52,711
Move to the stomach.

29
00:01:52,711 --> 00:01:57,773
Notice any holding, churning,
contraction, or ease.

30
00:02:06,773 --> 00:02:06,773
<break time="3s" />

31
00:02:06,773 --> 00:02:08,398
Move to the back.

32
00:02:08,398 --> 00:02:11,324
Notice support or strain.

33
00:02:11,324 --> 00:02:14,250
Move to the arms and hands.

34
00:02:14,250 --> 00:02:22,423
Notice whether they want to reach, hold,
push away, protect, or rest.

35
00:02:31,423 --> 00:02:31,423
<break time="3s" />

36
00:02:31,423 --> 00:02:35,603
Move to the hips, legs, and feet.

37
00:02:35,603 --> 00:02:38,714
Notice grounding or restlessness.

38
00:02:38,714 --> 00:02:43,126
Now choose one body area that called your
attention.

39
00:02:43,126 --> 00:02:48,327
Ask: Is there a part connected to this
sensation?

40
00:03:00,327 --> 00:03:00,327
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

41
00:03:00,327 --> 00:03:04,182
If yes, notice the part gently.

42
00:03:04,182 --> 00:03:07,944
If no, simply stay with the body area.

43
00:03:07,944 --> 00:03:11,938
Ask: What do you want me to know?

44
00:03:23,938 --> 00:03:23,938
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

45
00:03:23,938 --> 00:03:25,285
Listen.

46
00:03:43,285 --> 00:03:43,285
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

47
00:03:43,285 --> 00:03:48,533
Ask: What would help you feel one percent
safer?

48
00:04:00,533 --> 00:04:00,533
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

49
00:04:00,533 --> 00:04:08,551
Maybe breath, warmth, space, movement, a
hand nearby, a boundary, or a kind

50
00:04:08,551 --> 00:04:09,310
phrase.

51
00:04:09,310 --> 00:04:12,236
Offer that gently.

52
00:04:12,236 --> 00:04:15,580
Now notice if the sensation changes.

53
00:04:15,580 --> 00:04:23,382
It may soften. It may increase. It may
move. It may stay the same.

54
00:04:23,382 --> 00:04:26,819
All of that is okay.

55
00:04:26,819 --> 00:04:29,234
Thank your body for communicating.

56
00:04:29,234 --> 00:04:33,414
Thank any parts that allowed themselves
to be noticed.

57
00:04:33,414 --> 00:04:35,597
Take a slow breath in.

58
00:04:44,597 --> 00:04:44,597
<break time="3s" />

59
00:04:44,597 --> 00:04:46,547
And let it out.

60
00:04:46,547 --> 00:04:48,637
Return to the room.

61
00:04:57,637 --> 00:04:57,637
<break time="3s" />

62
00:04:57,637 --> 00:05:02,985
Carry with you the reminder that the body
can be listened to with patience, not

63
00:05:02,985 --> 00:05:03,396
force.

